org.tms.api

Interface BaseElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Cell, Column, Derivable, Row, Subset, Table, TableContext, TableElement, TableRowColumnElement

    public interface BaseElement
    This interface is the base from which all other TMS Table System interfaces extend. It contains methods and behavior common to all table elements, including Tables, Rows, Columns, Cells, and Subsets.

    Since:
    "1.0"
    Version:
    "1.1"
